  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Long term results after Ahmed glaucoma valve implantation for uncontrolled glaucoma are
      retrospectively examined.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The development of intraocular pressure, visual acuity, number of glaucoma medication, number
      of complications and necessity of revision operations after Ahmed glaucoma valve implantation
      for uncontrolled glaucoma is examined yearly for a period of 4 years.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
